us.description:
Leek Investment Company 2 is finally here, a new capital frenzy waiting for you to open!
1.New beautiful pixel graphics, up to 100 kinds of buildings, more than 200 kinds of icons;
2.Create value for the company, get promotion opportunities and a lot of commissions; acquire shares of the company and become the president of the company;
3.Real trading system (100x leveraged trading), up to thousands of random events, to make huge profits in the ever-changing market;
4.Awesome BTC mining system, simulating the BTC arithmetic system, hoarding a large number of mining machines to become a super miner;
5.Recruit talent to work for you and get double the results depending on the employee's occupation and talent;
6.Enter the leek club, get acquainted with industry elites and the world's richest people, and build your own business empire;
7.ICO/IPO system;
8.Extra large city map, city buildings can be acquired or upgraded;
9.Built-in multiple arithmetic games or DAPP;
10.Private garage, luxury car collection...

